  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/b6a7c8b787ce898ae9a9deb9a645b157.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/b6a7c8b787ce898ae9a9deb9a645b157.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive World War II inside a tank. Experience the most famous and greatest tank battles first-hand. Many historic battles await you, taking you all over the world. Experience the invasion of Poland, the attack on France, the war in the East and Africa, the liberation of Europe, the fall of Berlin and the Prague Uprising.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/d0b9be7936c2e775ce743999d1423042.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/d0b9be7936c2e775ce743999d1423042.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you'll find in the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Historical battles from the occupation of Czechoslovakia to the fall of Berlin and the Prague Uprising</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- you'll see the Soviet Union, North Africa, the mountains and the wastelands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- local multiplayer for two players - infantry, combined with tank</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- custom infantry and tank groups</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/5ee30443d712b6960d53883483aed642.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/5ee30443d712b6960d53883483aed642.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/722769cb260d379abd79d7190605d00e.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/722769cb260d379abd79d7190605d00e.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle Overview:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- The expulsion of the Czechs from the Sudetenland in 1938</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Invasion of Poland (1939)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Siege of Warsaw (1939)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of France (1940) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of Abbeville (1941)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Operation Barbarossa (1941)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of Moscow (1941)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Siege of Tobruk (1941) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of the Caucasus (1942)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of Stalingrad (1942-1943) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of the Kaserin Pass (1943)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of the Kursk Arch (1943)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Second Battle of El Alamein (1942)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of Caen (1944)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of the Ardennes (1945)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Battle of Berlin (1945)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Prague Uprising (1945)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/e810e15cc5a9b3c4f3d597e45e48306d.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/e810e15cc5a9b3c4f3d597e45e48306d.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/3482316b7c1562c6e4299de5510b7172.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/3482316b7c1562c6e4299de5510b7172.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/b6a7c8b787ce898ae9a9deb9a645b157.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/b6a7c8b787ce898ae9a9deb9a645b157.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=356 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive World War II inside a tank. Experience the most famous and greatest tank battles first-hand. Many historic battles await you, taking you all over the world. Experience the invasion of Poland, the attack on France, the war in the East and Africa, the liberation of Europe, the fall of Berlin and the Prague Uprising.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/d0b9be7936c2e775ce743999d1423042.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/d0b9be7936c2e775ce743999d1423042.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What you'll find in the game:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Historical battles from the occupation of Czechoslovakia to the fall of Berlin and the Prague Uprising</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- you'll see the Soviet Union, North Africa, the mountains and the wastelands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- local multiplayer for two players - infantry, combined with tank</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- custom infantry and tank groups</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/5ee30443d712b6960d53883483aed642.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https: