g/e810e15cc5a9b3c4f3d597e45e48306d.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras/3482316b7c1562c6e4299de5510b7172.avif?t=1740060595\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339340/extras_big/3482316b7c1562c6e4299de5510b7172.avif?t=1740060595 width=800 height=294 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
